  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个端到端加密的消息流程图，场景是教育场景下的课堂服务。用户通过客户端发消息，要经过Matrix服务器和联邦网络，最终到接收方。核心是要体现加密和解密的关键节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Client",
        "MatrixServer",
        "Federation",
        "Recipient",
        "End-to-End Encrypted Communication"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，教育场景。那加密是在客户端本地完成，还是交给服务器？还有持久化存储这块，数据库用什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "Encrypt",
        "MatrixServer",
        "Database"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "加密必须在Client端完成，标注为Education_ClassroomService。服务器只存密文，持久化用PostgreSQL。另外接收方要有独立的Client做解密，还要加上推送通知。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "Encrypt",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "MatrixServer",
        "Database",
        "PostgreSQL",
        "RecipientClient",
        "Push notification",
        "Decrypt message"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先把参与者列出来：User、Client、MatrixServer、Federation、Recipient，还有Database。流程起点是User在Client上撰写消息，然后Client本地加密。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
