    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，加密后发送到MatrixServer，服务器先自己存一份，再写到PostgreSQL，然后通过Federation转发到对方服务器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
