      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "RecipientClient解密之后，应该是展示给Recipient，不是Client自己看。还有Federation到Recipient的箭头，Recipient指的是用户还是服务器？这里容易歧义。",
